{"tid":884412,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"話說今晚我喺公屋試玩Trick-or-treating","createTime":"2018-10-31T14:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T16:02:06.000Z","uid":95489,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f055df51353feb054b0463468ebcbc7feba286aa","tid":884412,"uid":95489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T14:26:41.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n見今日係萬聖節就想比個6歲女感受下個氣氛<br />\n見外國都幾興玩Trick-or-treating <br />\n咁我就第一次想俾個女試下依種氣氛<br />\n就買咗勁多糖預備驚太多小朋友嚟啪門<br />\n跟住喺入夜時候幫個女化個鬼妀<br />\n我就同老婆留喺屋企等派糖俾小朋友<br />\n叫個女就去逐户逐户啪門<br />\n叫佢地一係俾糖個女，一係就搗蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知見咁耐都冇小朋友出嚟 亦冇人想開門咁<br />\n一係就唔理佢即閂門 <br />\n一係就話佢地講支那話聽唔明廣東話<br />\n當場呆咗 點解個個咁絕情<br />\n越諗越差嘅時候dump爆左部電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我想問邊到整機有得平d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf583bab63dc1346fcc35c0625140dbb6c7f6b93","tid":884412,"uid":170365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T14:27:52.000Z","msg":"柒撚少陣啦你"},{"pid":"d65deedc650338c9ff00031ebb513b12c6b347e8","tid":884412,"uid":95489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf583bab63dc1346fcc35c0625140dbb6c7f6b93","tid":884412,"uid":170365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T14:27:52.000Z","msg":"柒撚少陣啦你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T14:29:06.000Z","msg":"真係有心玩 尤其是我個女"},{"pid":"703661902097d295c19e3b2518c9f6d354264904","tid":884412,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T14:34:10.000Z","msg":"你有無屌過你個女？"},{"pid":"7817aaa6b7932cbaf0f2c63d4c3902b64ec650ad","tid":884412,"uid":62527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"703661902097d295c19e3b2518c9f6d354264904","tid":884412,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T14:34:10.000Z","msg":"你有無屌過你個女？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi